      "id": "files-folders-artboards-and-assets"
    }}>{`Files, folders, artboards and assets`}</h3>
    <p>{`No spaces or special characters are allowed to use in the filename. Use - instead of a space. Just use lowercase letters in filenames. American English is used for namings.`}</p>
