      <li parentName="ul"><strong parentName="li">{`Sketch (.sketch):`}</strong>{` Used to create assets/images for the specification for a better understanding of the UI`}</li>
      <li parentName="ul"><strong parentName="li">{`PNG (.png):`}</strong>{` Exported asset files from Sketch (size @1x). Will be linked in the Markdown file (how to).`}</li>
    </ul>
